<item>
            <title>[SOLR-467] Remove &apos;core&apos; options from solrj</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-467</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Remove the option to change cores for a SolrServer.  The core should be selected in the constructor &amp;#8211; for Http version, this is with the path, and the Embedded version can get registered with a name or SolrCore.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will require creating a new SolrServer for multi-core admin operations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
